snippet.title: Warhammer 40,000: Darktide - Official The Signal Trailer
snippet.description: Warhammer 40,000: Darktide's first content update, The Signal, brings the new mission Comms-Plex 154/2f, new weapons, and more to the game. Watch the trailer to see what to expect with The Signal content update.
